---
<section
  id="top"
  class="relative overflow-hidden min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center bg-paper pt-16"
>
  <div class="hero-depth" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">

    <p data-reveal class="font-body text-sm text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-10">
      Product Builder &amp; Software Engineer
    </p>

    <h1
      data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1"
      class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light text-ink mb-8"
      style="line-height: var(--leading-tight); max-width: 14ch;"
    >
      I don't wait for permission to build.
    </h1>

    <p data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2" class="font-body text-lg text-ink-muted mb-16" style="max-width: 52ch; line-height: var(--leading-normal);">
      I build thoughtful, production-ready software and leverage AI-assisted
      engineering to move from idea to deployment efficiently.
    </p>

    <a
      data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3"
      href="#proof"
      class="font-body text-sm text-accent hover:text-ink transition-colors"
      style="letter-spacing: 0.02em;"
    >
      See the work ↓
    </a>

  </div>
</section>
